 \"theIrelandstar\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 1500 metres\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In following up his gold in the 800m with another podium place, Wiffen became the first Irish male to win multiple medals at the same Olympics - and the first person since Michelle Smith 28 years ago.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9549418294612272, \"rank\": 0.02374342361331915, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 665, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.7896308802676635, \"rank\": 0.2209292737095758, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his gold\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"another podium place\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple medals\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"the same Olympics\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"the first person\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy but a bit disappointed at the same time,\\\" Wiffen said.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not be more pleased to be Olympic champion, but the bronze medal, I know you have to be pleased with any medal but when you hit gold the first time you are racing you do not want less than that.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"any medal\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I am happy.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have never had a medal at the Olympics before for men so to come away with two, I am very happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen beat America's Robert Finke and Italy's Gregorio Paltrinieri over 800m as he became Ireland's first male medallist in the pool and third overall after Michelle Smith and Mona McSharry.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Robert Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}, {\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.6302512083149768, \"rank\": 0.5002092756335548, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gregorio Paltrinieri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregorio_Paltrinieri\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1183, 